<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Mañana</title>

<!-- Tipografías elegantes -->
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@500;600&family=Inter:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f7f3ff, #efe7fb);
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  color: #3a2f4f;
}

/* CONTENEDOR */
.container {
  text-align: center;
}

/* TEXTO SUPERIOR */
.hint {
  margin-bottom: 18px;
  font-size: 16px;
  opacity: 0.8;
}

/* SOBRE */
.envelope {
  width: 260px;
  height: 170px;
  background: #fff;
  border-radius: 16px;
  position: relative;
  box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  cursor: pointer;
  overflow: hidden;
}

/* TAPA DEL SOBRE */
.envelope::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background: #f4c430;
  clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 50% 60%);
  transition: transform 0.6s ease;
  transform-origin: top;
}

/* TARJETA INTERIOR */
.card {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 16px;
  background: #ffffff;
  border-radius: 14px;
  padding: 22px 18px;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
  transform: translateY(80%);
  transition: transform 0.6s ease;
  text-align: center;
}

/* ABIERTO */
.envelope.open::before {
  transform: rotateX(180deg);
}

.envelope.open .card {
  transform: translateY(0);
}

/* TEXTO TARJETA */
h1 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 22px;
  margin: 0 0 10px 0;
}

.dots {
  margin-bottom: 14px;
  font-size: 20px;
}

p {
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin: 0;
}

.emojis {
  margin-top: 14px;
  font-size: 22px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">
  <div class="hint">Toca el sobre 💛</div>

  <div class="envelope" onclick="this.classList.toggle('open')">
    <div class="card">
      <h1>Mañana</h1>

      <div class="dots">💛 🎁 🎂</div>

      <p>
        Si tú estás tranquila, yo no tanto 😅<br>
        Mañana cumple años alguien importante.
      </p>

      <div class="emojis">🌻 💛</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
